<HEADLINE> Drugs Destroyed In East China City </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SUZHOU, June 3 (Xinhua) -- A total of 6.57 kg of heroin and 10.
75 kg of opium was burnt in the scenic site Suzhou in east China's
Jiangsu Province today.
</P>
<P>
Statistics show that since 1999, the city has exposed 1084 drug-
trafficking cases and arrested 896 drug dealers. 
</P>
