country will be allowed to withdraw 3,000 dinar from his foreign
currency account at an exchange rate of 20 dinar against one
Deutsche mark, Pessich told reporters. And as from July 1, the
depositors can each withdraw 150 marks in foreign exchange, he
added. (Yugoslavia-Foreign Exchange)
