<TEXT>
<P>
JAKARTA, June 3 (Xinhua) -- Indonesian rising star Taufik
Hidayat has vowed to retain the Indonesia Open badminton
championship title that he won last year in Bali.
</P>
<P>
This year's tournament will be held at Senayan indoor stadium
in Jakarta from July 19 to 23.
</P>
<P>
