<HEADLINE> Guatemalan President To Visit Mexico, U.S., Japan </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MEXICO CITY, June 3 (Xinhua) -- Guatemalan President Alfonso
Portillo is scheduled to visit Mexico, the United States and Japan,
Guatemalan Foreign Minister Gabriel Orellana announced Saturday.
</P>
<P>
The visits, to occur in the next weeks, will include meetings
with the heads of state of the three nations, said Orellana,
according to reports from Guatemala City.
