presidents of Guatemala, El Salvador and Honduras to sign on June
29 or 30 in Mexico City the free trade agreement among the four
countries.
</P>
<P>
Portillo will meet with Zedillo during his visit to Mexico, and
with U.S. President Bill Clinton when he visits the United States.
